{{Politics of Kazakhstan}}
The '''Agrarian Party of Kazakhstan''' (''Qazaqstan Agrarlyq Parti'i'asy'') is a [[political party]] in [[Kazakhstan]]. 
At the last [[legislative]] [[elections in Kazakhstan|elections]], 19 September and 3 October 2004, the party was part of the [[Agrarian and Industrial Union of Workers Bloc]], that won 7.1% of the popular vote and 11 out of 77 seats.

